# Overview

**UMAC (Unified Military Analytics and Comparison)** is a data analytics platform designed to evaluate and compare the military capabilities of **140+ countries using 2025 defense data**.

The system automates the pipeline from **web data collection to interactive Power BI dashboards**, enabling analysts to examine global defense capabilities, compare countries, and analyze strategic military trends.

The dataset includes more than **50 defense indicators**, including:

- Military manpower
- Air, land, and naval equipment
- Defense budgets
- Global power rankings
- Economic and population metrics

---

# Architecture

## System Workflow

```
Raw Web Data (Global Firepower)
        │
        ▼
Python Web Scraper
(BeautifulSoup + Requests)
        │
        ▼
Raw Dataset
military_raw_data.csv
        │
        ▼
Data Cleaning & KPI Engineering
(Pandas + NumPy)
        │
        ▼
Final Dataset
military_final.csv
        │
        ▼
Power BI Dashboard
Interactive Military Analytics
```

